      "content": "For maximum authority, focus on a polished and tailored appearance that aligns with your company's established culture. Clothing should be impeccably maintained, featuring sharp lines and high-quality fabrics to convey attention to detail. Grooming should be understated yet meticulous, ensuring hair and facial hair are neat, as this signals discipline and control. Ultimately, the goal is to look authoritative, not distracting.",
