    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Could you get a bit more specific though? Like, what are some concrete examples of hair styles or grooming habits that might be seen as \"distracting\" or \"less professional\" in a boardroom setting? I want to make sure my team knows exactly where the line is.",
