      "content": "In a boardroom, overly flamboyant or trendy hairstyles can be distracting; conservative, well-kept styles are best. Excessive or brightly colored hair dye should be avoided as it draws undue attention. Similarly, overly elaborate or heavily perfumed scents are unprofessional, as they can be off-putting to others. The general rule is that your appearance should support your message, not overshadow it.",
