      "content": "Got it. I'm also thinking about diversity in the leadership team. Some of our executives have more textured, natural hair, or might wear religious head coverings like a hijab or a turban. Should we be advising them to stick to more \"conservative\" or \"standard\" styles to ensure they aren't seen as a distraction during these high-stakes meetings?",
